msgstr "Au lieu de tomber, vous descendez gracieusement."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_potions/potions.lua:550
msgid "Decreases damage taken at the cost of speed."
msgstr "Diminue les dégâts reçus aux dépends de la vitesse."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_potions/potions.lua:570
msgid "Increases luck."
msgstr "Augmente la chance."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_potions/potions.lua:582
msgid "Decreases luck."
